import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

# Ak je TM_ref prechodová matica vytvorená zo súboru krakatit.txt, premenujeme si ju na TM kvôli kompatibilite
TM = TM_ref

# Základné štatistiky
print("✅ Štatistiky prechodovej matice:")
print("max:", np.max(TM))
lowest = np.min(TM)
print("lowest:", lowest)
second_lowest = sorted(set(TM.flatten()))[1]
print("second lowest:", second_lowest)
print("sum:", np.sum(TM))
quartiles = np.quantile(TM, [0, 0.25, 0.5, 0.75, 1])
print("quartiles:", quartiles)

# Vykreslenie troch heatmáp
fig, axes = plt.subplots(1, 3, figsize=(18, 5))

alphabet_labels = list("ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ_")
ticks = list(range(len(alphabet_labels)))

# Heatmap 1: surové hodnoty
plt.sca(axes[0])
plt.imshow(TM, cmap='turbo')
plt.title("Transition matrix heatmap (raw)")
plt.xticks(ticks=ticks, labels=alphabet_labels)
plt.yticks(ticks=ticks, labels=alphabet_labels)
plt.colorbar()

# Heatmap 2: orezané hodnoty (pre lepší kontrast)
plt.sca(axes[1])
plt.imshow(TM, cmap='turbo', vmax=quartiles[3])
plt.title("Transition matrix heatmap - flattened")
plt.xticks(ticks=ticks, labels=alphabet_labels)
plt.yticks(ticks=ticks, labels=alphabet_labels)
plt.colorbar()

# Heatmap 3: výskyt bigramov (áno/nie)
plt.sca(axes[2])
plt.imshow(TM, cmap='coolwarm', vmin=lowest, vmax=second_lowest)
plt.title("Transition matrix heatmap - occurences")
plt.xticks(ticks=ticks, labels=alphabet_labels)
plt.yticks(ticks=ticks, labels=alphabet_labels)
cbar = plt.colorbar()
cbar.set_ticks([lowest, second_lowest])
cbar.set_ticklabels(["No", "Yes"])

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

from mh_decipher import mh_algorithm
# Spracuj všetky súbory v priečinku
for filename in test_files:
    if not filename.endswith("_ciphertext.txt"):
        continue

    parts = filename.split('_')
    length = parts[1]
    sample_id = parts[3].split('.')[0]

    with open(os.path.join(input_dir, filename), "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        ciphertext = f.read().strip()

    # Spusti algoritmus
    start_key = random.sample(alphabet, len(alphabet))
    best_key, decrypted_text, best_score = prolom_substitute(
        ciphertext, TM_ref, iter=20000, start_key=start_key, alphabet=alphabet
    )

    # Ulož výstup do ../export/
    plaintext_path = os.path.join(output_dir, f"text_{length}_sample_{sample_id}_plaintext.txt")
    key_path = os.path.join(output_dir, f"text_{length}_sample_{sample_id}_key.txt")

    with open(plaintext_path, "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        f.write(decrypted_text)

    with open(key_path, "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        f.write(''.join(best_key))

    print(f"✅ Hotovo: sample {sample_id} spracovaný.")
    
    plt.plot(mh_algorithm.plausabilities)
    plt.title("Plausabilities for "+filename)
    plt.show()
